  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fertilizer is distributed to the districts as follows",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Agricultural Services Development mentioned that the bulk distribution of urea fertilizer given to Sri Lanka by the Government of India is currently being done very successfully.",
        "102.5 metric tons of urea fertilizer has been supplied to Polonnaruwa district, 196.84 metric tons to Hambantota district, 63 metric tons to Monaragala district, and 25 metric tons to Matale district.",
        "The Department of Agricultural Development says that the fertilizer distribution will be done for the next few days. These fertilizer distribution activities are carried out by the two government-owned fertilizer companies Lanka Fertilizer Company and Lanka Commercial Fertilizer Company."
      ],
